{"tid":604761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個因爲流鼻血而尷尬嘅經歷","createTime":"2018-03-25T05:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T13:44:45.000Z","uid":136625,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"625cf5729a1b9ba32bf5d6919bf04d8a02aa1182","tid":604761,"uid":136625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:02:44.000Z","msg":"講下背景先 小弟因為天生鼻膜薄 自細好易流鼻血 可以乜都冇做而無啦啦流鼻血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁話說我有一次去游水勁多人 之後比個廢中游游下水踢中左個鼻  之後就開始猛咁流鼻血 最後好尷尬咁用手掩住個鼻 成手血咁上水止血 見到成個泳池有某部份係我啲鼻血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個係以前中學果陣係禮堂考試 做做下卷feel到個鼻有野要流出黎 起初以為係流鼻水 最後有滴鼻血滴左落份卷到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果陣又冇紙巾 最後又係成手血尷尷尬尬咁沖左去廁所 自此有個花名叫鼻血哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c478035767769169aa401894e4918ba58e8c480","tid":604761,"uid":136625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:23:49.000Z","msg":"連登仔冇人會流鼻血？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51c7994e6483304a6a98e5bf8e8b7631b3f1895","tid":604761,"uid":136625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:45:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091ea2c4deabef24ccaa83171dbb06ceb0854d6f","tid":604761,"uid":56690,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:48:23.000Z","msg":"去廁所流緊鼻血果陣打乞嚏<br />\n成塊鏡都係血點<br />\n隔離個人即刻彈開幾米<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13368aba6a158bf80710b39024467f0b1ad3cb00","tid":604761,"uid":32279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:53:45.000Z","msg":"喺日本排梗隊等餐廳食<br />\n無徵兆下就流<br />\n成手血叫女朋友搵紙巾點知用晒<br />\n要問前面個日本媽媽借<br />\n已經兜到成手都係血<br />\n佢見到個反應好似卡通人物咁有啲浮誇<br />\n大嗌左一聲 然後搵紙巾比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他人全部望住我"},{"pid":"8e87909b48666e7a2c835d3628cdc74951a96f46","tid":604761,"uid":64308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"中學既時候 上緊堂流鼻血所以衝去廁所<br />\n點知經過人地班房門口既時候<br />\n唔小心飛咗隻鞋出去人地門口<br />\n嗰時仲要秋天冇開冷氣所以打開道門<br />\n我一路掩住個鼻一路用穿返隻鞋<br />\n成班人大笑 柒到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最尾搞掂哂之後 我特登落一層<br />\n喺第二邊上返去<br />\n點知小息比嗰班人問我去廁所咁耐搞乜<br />\n原來佢地一直捕住我行返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225245aeba3a6b723154a31ced712f1b630b0d15","tid":604761,"uid":1767,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:52:10.000Z","msg":"由小到大都無流過鼻血<br />\n不過有個frd經常流鼻血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高峰時期一個星期流三四次<br />\n覺得佢好無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99302455d8fad4a590e2a60f402111a39f497721","tid":604761,"uid":128192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:11:20.000Z","msg":"食完飯行緊返學校個陣流鼻血 嗱嗱聲跑返去學校地下廁所 點知撞到個f1仔 鼻血噴曬落自己件衫 用水洗唔走 仲要擴大咗個血漬 返到班房啲人問我頭先去劈友?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d6471be1b2fe49f3d92550b73bad324d507bd8","tid":604761,"uid":136625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:18:02.000Z","msg":"係咪開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef49cdcc7c8e7f7ae6ad3ca2d525170fcbb4aaf","tid":604761,"uid":52503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"091ea2c4deabef24ccaa83171dbb06ceb0854d6f","tid":604761,"uid":56690,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:48:23.000Z","msg":"去廁所流緊鼻血果陣打乞嚏<br />\n成塊鏡都係血點<br />\n隔離個人即刻彈開幾米<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:20:59.000Z","msg":"我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0393c70b4c9c70cfa714312e9d90e00bd8e749af","tid":604761,"uid":136625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:30:26.000Z","msg":"不過沖涼嗰陣流鼻血係最爽 我會等流晒先出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3a0e5e4c9fb299c8d4cf3095cedda4fa785f74","tid":604761,"uid":5570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:44:45.000Z","msg":"唯一一次流鼻血係 細細個比啊哥打爆左個鼻之後係咁流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無試個又流血又尷尬經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}